snippet: The musicians of New Multitudes have found inspiration in the words of Woody Guthrie. On Wednesday night, they appeared at Webster Hall to perform the songs they had written, drawn from Guthrie’s writing.
abstract: Nate Chinen reviews performance by band New Multitudes at Webster Hall.
lead_paragraph: The musicians of New Multitudes have found inspiration in the words of Woody Guthrie. On Wednesday night, they appeared at Webster Hall to perform the songs they had written, drawn from Guthrie’s writing.
